title: Texas Flip and Move S02E13 Airstream vs House on Wheels PDTV.x26
description:
Texas Flip and Move - Season 2, Episode 13




Randy's Vintage Airstream Dream vs. Young Guns' Rolling Retreat

Randy gets a bargain on a vintage 31 foot 1972 Airstream travel trailer. It's not exactly a house, but Randy knows that there is a good market for these once they've been renovated. Cody scores a large house, but has to knock it down when he can't get anyone to move it. All is not lost when he takes a small shed from the back yard and uses it to make an adorable tiny house on wheels that is completely portable.




Original Air Date: 11-Dec-2015
